<p>
<note n="0237002" resp="#resp1" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0237002">佛說【大】＊，〔－〕【元】【明】＊</note>
<note n="0237003" resp="#resp1" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0237003">藏【大】，藏法師【宋】【明】【宮】</note>
